{
  "name": "Witch Bolt",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"flex-even column\" data-markdown=\"1\">\n<div class=\"item d-flex flex-wrap\" data-markdown=\"1\">\n<div class=\"flex-even column\" data-markdown=\"1\">\n<p>A beam of crackling, blue energy lances out toward a creature within range, forming a sustained arc of electricity between you and the target. Make a ranged spell attack against that creature. On a hit, the target takes 1d12 points of electricity damage. Each round you sustain the spell thereafter, you deal an additional @Damage[1d12[electricity]] damage to the target. The spell ends if the target is ever outside the spell's range or if you lose the line of effect.</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The initial damage increases by 1d12.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
